item.title: First post
item.description: Hello and welcome! I set up this website to share my thoughts. It’s empty for now but I’ll be sure to start uploading content soon. I’m using Hugo and GitHub Pages which helps spin up static websites a lot. I’m hoping that Hugo will also have nice support for hosting static javascript/python code which would allow me to add visualisations. Thanks for visiting.

item.title: About me
item.description: Hello, my name is Tautvydas. I’m a data scientist and a geek living in Zurich. I dabble with ideas and use computers to solve them. Afterward, when I have some time I write them up here. If you are interested in my professional history check out my CV. Interests Machine learning Photography Sailing Robotics Reinforcement learning Contact me You can reach out to me at tautvydas.misiunas (at) gmail.com
